name: Royal Agro Green Foods Industries Pvt. Ltd.
overview: Incepted in the year 2007, we, “Royal Agro Green Foods Industries Pvt. Ltd.”, are counted amidst the distinguished organizations which are engaged in manufacturing, trading, supplying and exporting of an exemplary range of Indian Rice, Food Grains, Indian Spices and Sugar. Offered assortment includes 1121 Basmati Rice, Andhra Ponni Rice, Golden Sella Rice, Sona Masuri Rice, Green Beans and Soybean Meal. Additionally, to fulfill the variegated requirements of our clients, we are providing them Skinned and Split White Lentils, Split Green Pigeon Peas, Yellow Split Peas, Skimmed Milk Powder, Extra Neutral Alcohol, Poultry Feed and various other products. Our products are processed in hygienic conditions so as to ensure their quality in tune with the international food safety standards. We provide these products to the clients in air tight packagings to maintain their quality and ensure longer shelf life. Offered products are widely used for making various types of vegetarian and non-vegetarian dishes of Indian, Arabic, Cuban and numerous other origins
